Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧 今天我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现身了啊恶魔 你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天！ 大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣！ 搭讪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游泳吧 奥村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小出云 快换衣服 换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}我最爱大海了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs67.5}来来 快点~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰满的大姐姐们就在面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得帮忙做铁板乌贼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把灵魂出卖给恶魔也物有所值的美味铁板乌贼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥村同学可真积极
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 反正不讨厌干这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全卖不动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看上去这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝一点行吗 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 要卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是奥村同学的使魔Cait Sith吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是任务吧 所以带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里像任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用寻找做除魔药品的海草当借口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里才是主战场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住的民宅和海边的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那有鬓角的夫人老家经营的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定去多摩川开采囀石的小坊和小猫丸更爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去石头那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 能好好呆会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没个漂亮女孩子在卖不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少小出云能更主动帮下忙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我们协调性不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说你今天泳衣很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说些什么 我不是已经帮忙烧乌贼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外你不会觉得我适合招揽顾客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经游够了 好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好轮流游泳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傲 一点娇都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 卖得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么好心的学生 我可真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:32.29,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0)\pos(1564.5,1065)}深海的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么协调性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是难得的惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 腿抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚 滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心想给你做人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸胸 滥用暴力 还要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明救了你 还这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分啊 硬脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢 看这个肿包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下巴更…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这小孩胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩 我叫洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太小了没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子是小 但我老爹说了 男人只要那地方大就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 内心强大不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海被染黑时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现跟小山一样大的恶魔 摧毁村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方自古流传的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,400年前这间寺庙的住持画的彩马匾额
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs63}*彩马匾额：为祈祷神灵佛主的木板画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变黑的大海是因为乌贼喷墨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这只是过去的传说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上半年前大海变黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个渔民为了驱除恶魔出海了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他现在还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特地跑到这听恶魔的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把打倒它当做我们的首次任务 听起来多酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去哪了 我们很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过脑袋真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都看到我们了 还不让下路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不 老爹说过 男人要走笔直的路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是个比喻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是笔直地走不会迷路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道宠物店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面写着宠物店的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说… 我迷路了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要给当地人指路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直在这买东西的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗不适应夏天的炎热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适应？ 难道平时都带着狗过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个大路痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爹比这还厉害 是个更加彻底的路痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在说你父亲的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾是个很厉害的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前他出海就没回来 一直在追赶它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是说？ 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹被它干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定要打倒那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生乌贼鱼片 乌贼挂面 乌贼南蛮煮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs63}*南蛮煮：指16世纪由葡萄牙传入日本的欧式料理 将鱼肉和芥末放在一起煮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼纳豆 乌贼墨意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊 全是乌贼料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 全是乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 据说最近海里捞上来的全是乌贼 大家都很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因此足够我们猛吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪卖不出去 铁板乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉肯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深海的恶魔中 要说喷射墨汁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在挪威的博物志中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关于克拉肯将整片大海染黑的记载
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞上来的全是乌贼 也是因为它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是克拉肯 有打倒它的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说 深海恶魔的致死节是在以弗所书第一章的18节里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs63}*以弗所书：出自圣经新约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但手段有限 一个小孩子是不可能打倒它的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 真没办法 小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有点事出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天会有更正经的工作 海边的事不用做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫正经工作啊 把我们当临时工了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说又提到小猫咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说… 奥村同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一天守着那个叫洋平的孩子 别轻易让他去找恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂抹的药膏 老爹出海时经常带着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有效 涂在包上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这个特地来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 回去的路是哪条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大海又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也发现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他别瞎想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小出云？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 好歹我被他救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌自不量力的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不用换班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小出云这么在意别人可真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上也一直守着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等 直到它出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是恶魔 你一个人是干不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多嘴多舌 它是老爹的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定要打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真执着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不掂量下自己的力量独自解决 也会有办不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看你我就觉得丢脸 自不量力自讨苦吃的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那受到打击你就会退缩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹说过了 老是说消极的事是因为自信不够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己犹豫了 想让别人也犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我早就不再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不挺好吗 再怎么迷路也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心决定的事就不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是老爹说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想老爹碰到那恶魔时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是毫不犹豫地决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不会犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要像老爹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋平君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恶魔啊 是恶魔喷的墨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 佛经 佛经
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是佛经 是咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不会是想打倒它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不管它 可能就这样登陆 胡作非为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们必须在那孩子之前动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣徒应继承上帝的国家 是何等的荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝力量强大的行动 将努力的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们信仰之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是个聋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不是长着那么大的耳朵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是鳍 连小孩都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳍？ 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 跟怪兽电影一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗 猫它…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑 怎么了 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs67.5}眼花了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫一碰到生乌贼 就会浑身无力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢 来这了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 这么紧要关头还迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻荷神惶恐惶恐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 小出云
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了 离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小孩子努力就能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了打倒它 为了给老爹报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋平 洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs67.5}洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓角…椿薫老师 您去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是克拉肯 得做好应对 调查了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是没什么危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后不知道怎么回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年内到过无人岛 一直漂流着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和它一起寻找日本 但这家伙也是个大路痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹 这家伙不是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋平 让内心更柔软一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗的时候我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有乌贼 它的内心和身体一样柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的内心已经完全转变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但男人一旦决定要打倒它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 洋平 要像乌贼的生鱼片一样率真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人也要有勇气改变已经决定的事 男人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹 我觉得获得新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 洋平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔也有改过自新的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想教会你们这点 看来让你们来这是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}太差劲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来送我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我家的小白 可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个眉毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 眉毛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然笑起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能笑笑了 全是无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于想陪他玩玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊 很可爱啊 杜山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天吗 裙子太短了吧
